		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64466605"><p>Mass production reduces costs through factors beyond just scale: people figure out substitutions, simplifications, human factor improvements, and more.  As someone else pointed out, these mechanisms kick in for a wide variety of artifacts, so saying "nuclear reactor are (also) different" doesn't distinguish them.</p></div>
	</div>

